# Integrating {{ isa_name }} into LLVM

Generated by [isa-archive](https://github.com/your-org/isa-archive).

## Prerequisites

- LLVM source tree (18.x or later recommended)
- CMake 3.20+, Ninja, C++17 compiler

## Quick start

```bash
# 1. Integrate the generated target
bash patch_llvm.sh /path/to/llvm-project

# 2. Configure — build only this target to keep build times short
cmake -G Ninja -B /tmp/llvm-build \
      -DLLVM_TARGETS_TO_BUILD="{{ ISA }}" \
      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release \
      /path/to/llvm-project/llvm

# 3. Build llc
ninja -C /tmp/llvm-build llc

# 4. Compile LLVM IR
/tmp/llvm-build/bin/llc -march={{ isa_name }} input.ll -o output.s
```

