## Extending the backend

- **New instructions**: add entries to `{{ ISA }}InstrInfo.td`
- **Custom lowering**: implement `{{ ISA }}ISelLowering::LowerOperation` for new `ISD::` nodes
- **Relocations**: extend `{{ ISA }}ELFObjectWriter::getRelocType`
- **Scheduling**: fill in `{{ ISA }}Schedule.td` with measured latencies

